column12: > env indicator: environmental indicator (GHGe=GHG emissions (MtCO2-eq), land=cropland use (1000 km2), water=bluewater use (km3), nitr=nitrogen application (GgN), nitrogen application and fixation (nitr_sfert, GgN), nitrogen surplus (nitr_splus, GgN), phos=phosphorus application (GgP)
> tech_scn: technology scenario, including benchmark technologies (BMK), technological change of medium ambition (TECH), and technological change of high ambition (TECH_p)
> waste_scn: waste scenario, including no changes to food loss and waste (full_w), and halving of food loss and waste (half_w)

> diet_scn: diet scenarios, including benchmark diets (BMK), flexitarian diets (FLX), with high milk consumption (FLX_hmilk) or with high red-meat consumption (FLX_hredmeat), pescatarian diets (PSC), vegetarian diets (VEG), vegan diets (VGN)
> kcal_scn: calorie scenario, including 2500 kcal/d representative of active adults, and 2100 kcal/d representative of total population average
> measure: absolute values (abs), absolute changes (chg), percentage changes (pct), absolute changes relative to 2010 (chg_2010), percentage changes relative to 2010 (pct_2010)
> waste_scn: waste scenario, including no changes to food loss and waste (full_w), and halving of food loss and waste (half_w)
> region: regions and countries, including high-income (HIC), upper middle-income (UMC), lower middle-income (LMC), low-income (LIC), and all regions (all-r)
> year: year of analysis, including 2010, 2030, and 2050
